const formatter = new Intl.NumberFormat('en-US', { style: 'currency', currency: 'USD', minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 }) const ResultTable = (props) => { return ( {props.data.map(yearData => ( ))}
Year Total Savings Interest (Year) Total Interest Invested Capital
{yearData.year} {formatter.format(yearData.savingsEndOfYear)} {formatter.format(yearData.yearlyInterest)} {yearData.savingsEndOfYear - props.initialInvestment- yearData.yearlyContribution * yearData.year} {props.initialInvestment + yearData.yearlyContribution * yearData.year}
